what keeps sending /complete autokill to lastocean

summary: Investigated repeated /complete autokill events in lastocean service
Traced potential source of automatic completion triggers
Moved auto-complete toggle into StatusActionBadge dropdown for improved control

suggestedTasks.title: Implement logging for unexpected /complete autokill events
suggestedTasks.description:
Add comprehensive logging mechanism to track and diagnose why /complete events are being triggered unexpectedly in lastocean service. Create a detailed event trace that captures timestamp, triggering component, and context of each autokill event.

Focus on components related to StatusActionBadge and task completion workflows to identify the root cause of unintended completions.
suggestedTasks.reason: Current investigation revealed potential systemic issue with task completion triggers
